<H2>PortableApps.com Data</H2>
To select only the Data folders of your PortableApps folder you need the following rules:<p>
<strong>Folders to exclude:</strong>
<pre>\\PortableApps</pre><P>
<strong>Locations to include:</strong>
<pre>\\Data</pre><p>
<P>
Simply save these two strings into a new set of Rules and you can them use them in Sync, Backup or Secure by selecting them in the drop down box.
</PRE>
